    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="checkpoint.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="pcontainer">
    <p>The vibrant city buzzed with energy as people filled the streets, going about their daily routines. Cars honked their horns amidst the chaotic traffic, while pedestrians hurriedly navigated the crowded sidewalks. The aroma of freshly brewed coffee wafted from the corner caf√©, enticing passersby with its rich scent. Meanwhile, the distant sound of a street performer's guitar added a melodic touch to the urban symphony. Towering skyscrapers adorned the skyline, reflecting the sunlight and casting shadows on the bustling city below. Shop windows showcased a myriad of products, enticing shoppers with their colorful displays. Laughter and conversation spilled out from open-air restaurants, where patrons savored delicious meals and shared moments of joy. Amidst the hustle and bustle, street vendors sold their wares, offering tantalizing street food and unique handcrafted items. The city's diversity was evident in its multicultural neighborhoods, each with its own distinct charm and character. From the historic landmarks to the hidden alleyways, every corner held a story waiting to be discovered. As day turned into night, the city transformed, with neon lights illuminating the streets and casting an enchanting glow. The energy of the city never waned, as it continued to thrive with life, constantly evolving and embracing the ever-changing world around it.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- <div class="square">
        <div class="circle"></div>
    </div> -->
</body>
</html> 

CSS:

.pcontainer{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
